    "Generative AI models can be used in various applications across a wide range of industries, such as art, writing, software development, healthcare, finance, gaming, marketing, and fashion [1][4] [5].Generative AI starts with a prompt that could be in the form of text, an image, a video, a design, musical notes, or any input that the AI system can process [2].",
